short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Generating analytics reports for Wolt orders

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ordering food becomes a daily routine for many people during the pandemic.
This essential tool provides you with the visibility into how many food orders you make and how much you spend on a monthly and annually basis.
